<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="excite-vt">excite <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'saɪt/    美 /ɪk'saɪt/  </p>
<p>[不用于进行时]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使兴奋；使激动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The news excited me very much. 
这消息让我很兴奋。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>激起；引起：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The museum offers a variety of activities to <strong>excite</strong> your kids' <strong>interest</strong>.
博物馆提供很多活动来激发孩子们的兴趣。</p><footer>2012 全国改</footer></div></div>